  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"If you could do anything before you graduate, what would you do?\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/60a7b63f4c780f3263f68dbf45c79736.poster.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/60a7b63f4c780f3263f68dbf45c79736.webm?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/60a7b63f4c780f3263f68dbf45c79736.mp4?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>In Between All Times is a cinematic visual novel about a graduate student's struggles in finding purpose and identity, set in a surreal future in the stars.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graduation looms around the corner for the protagonist in his final year of university, when he meets a mysterious campus ghost in his usually empty clubroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ghost, named Byeol, decides to join the club and forms a peculiar relationship with him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together in this Creative Writing Club, they set out to complete a small goal: to complete a short story before graduation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And so, in between all times...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"A story about one's very personal yet confusing creative journey.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/51a2dc66b35a8d98fa2c79de2ca99b5b.avif?t=1759220371\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A campus life in the vast reaches of the galaxy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy your last year on a campus set in space, experience familiar moments of life in an unfamiliar world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/3ca35e01bfbd64590d0c1ff7ace4cfc7.poster.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/3ca35e01bfbd64590d0c1ff7ace4cfc7.webm?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/3ca35e01bfbd64590d0c1ff7ace4cfc7.mp4?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse yourself with a variety of visuals and motion graphics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From beautiful, fully-illustrated CGs, to comic panels and extensive use of motion graphics, the visuals will help you dive into the world of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/6b135a7cc8889b6661c582f9f065c1fb.poster.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/6b135a7cc8889b6661c582f9f065c1fb.webm?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/6b135a7cc8889b6661c582f9f065c1fb.mp4?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/13e99904ff37f0886c8b9bbb50b1e567.poster.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/13e99904ff37f0886c8b9bbb50b1e567.webm?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/13e99904ff37f0886c8b9bbb50b1e567.mp4?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A linear story - a kinetic novel</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/87d915e0cc4dd3263fcdef62cf4193ae.poster.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/87d915e0cc4dd3263fcdef62cf4193ae.webm?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/87d915e0cc4dd3263fcdef62cf4193ae.mp4?t=1759220371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOPMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2917740/extras/e6dbcf060b4676979a54cc5775dd5e74.avif?t=1759220371\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Studio Elysian is a South Korean story-based game development team founded in 2022.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The team consists of a diverse range of talents throughout Korea, with backgrounds ranging from film production to comics, music videos and Vocaloid song production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'In Between All Times' is their 2nd official Visual Novel Title.</p>",
